2011-08-12  Zachary Dovel  <pizzach@gmail.com>

	* Made gWaei object orented.  All objects are created/freed using *_new/*_free commands.
	* The program now uses much less memory.
  * Updated the interface a bit more to comply better with Gnome 3
	* NCurses interface has become unsupported
	* Hardcore valgrind checking for memory leaks
	* Program defaults to hitting enter for searches instead of automatically
	updated
	* Moved dconf schemas position to org/gnome/gwaei
	* The program should use less CPU when idle now thanks to better use of
	signals
	* Various fixes for compiling under mingw32 for windows

